### Get All Stores
GET {{baseUrl}}/stores?organization_id=1&page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### Get Store by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/stores/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### üö® STORE DASHBOARD - Key FASE2 Feature
